author: namapane
body:
Removing the following table sets, that are no longer in use in CMSSW since later releases in the 93X series:
- grid_1103l_071212_3t
- grid_1103l_071212_3_5t
- grid_1103l_071212_3_8t
- grid_120812_3_8t_v7_large
- grid_120812_3_8t_v7_small
- grid_130503_3_8t_v9_large
- grid_130503_3_8t_v9_small
- grid_1103l_090322_3_8t 

Only table sets that are still relevant in CMSSW_11_X are kept unchanged:
- grid_11103l_071212_2t
- grid_11103l_071212_4t
- grid_160812_3t
- grid_160812_3_5t
- grid_160812_3_8t
- grid_160812_3_8t_Run1 

No new file is added.
title: Remove table sets that are no longer used since 93X or earlier
